1.0 Workflow Basics

lm_model <- 
  linear_reg() |> 
  set_engine("lm")

lm_wflow <- 
  workflow() |> 
  add_model(lm_model) |> 
  add_formula(Sale_Price ~ Longitude + Latitude)
lm_fit <-  fit(lm_wflow, ames_train)
